  "title": "ORDER FULFILMENT SPECIALIST",
  "description": "<h3>Winner of E50 Awards 2021, 2022 &amp; 2023</h3>\n<h3>One of Singapore’s Fastest-Growing Companies 2022</h3>\n<p><u><strong>Job Description</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Deal directly with customers either by telephone, electronically or face to face</li>\n  <li>Respond promptly, handle and resolve customer inquiries, complaints</li>\n  <li>Obtain and evaluate all relevant information to handle product and service inquiries</li>\n  <li>Provide pricing and delivery information</li>\n  <li>Process orders and requests</li>\n  <li>Organize workflow to meet customer time frames</li>\n  <li>Direct requests and unresolved issues to the designated resource</li>\n  <li>Keep records of customer interactions and transactions</li>\n  <li>Manage administration</li>\n  <li>Support, communicate and coordinate with Sales team and internal departments</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u><strong>Requirements</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Min GCE ‘N’ or ‘O’ Level or equivalent</li>\n  <li>Bilingual in English and Mandarin to interact with Mandarin speaking customers</li>\n  <li>Experience in sales support / customer service would be an added advantage</li>\n  <li>Knowledge of customer service principles and practices</li>\n  <li>Customer Service Oriented</li>\n  <li>Dedicated team player with ability to work under pressure and deliver results</li>\n  <li>A meticulous and responsible employee</li>\n  <li>Able to work independently with minimum supervision</li>\n  <li>Knowledge of relevant computer applications</li>\n  <li>Able to work independently</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>",
